  <title>Estabeleza o nome do seu computador</title>

  <p>You can change the name your computer uses to display itself to other
  computers or devices, on the network or over Bluetooth.</p>

  <steps>
    <title>Para cambiar o nome do seu computador:</title>
    <item>
      <p>Open the <gui xref="shell-introduction#activities">Activities</gui> overview and
      start typing <gui>Sharing</gui>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Prema en <gui>Compartici√≥n</gui> no lateral dereito.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Edit the text below <gui>Computer Name</gui> to change the name your
      computer displays on the network.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

